data.title: Cooley Law School Distinguished Student Award
data.meta_description: Distinguished Student Award Awarded three times a year since 1980, the Distinguished Student Award seeks to honor those graduating students who have displayed high standards throughout their law school careers.  Support these Awards - Ways to Give
data.text:
In corde hominum est anima legis. | The spirit of the law is in the human heart.
